metadata.name: Isekai #1 - Koo
metadata.description: Isekai Meta is a story and community-driven, hand-drawn NFT collection + metaverse brand that taps into the foundational human need to connect with others through story. Heavily influenced by pop culture, lo-fi aesthetics, and Japanese anime. The project and the community behind it intends to spark a new age of storytelling through web3 and NFTs.
